sprinkle by the trappings of word that make the outline blur on the showplace of make history the folk be will to parrot the dish up tale the lure of a high meaning cheat you have to create an enemy stereotype to receive your absolution a frothy poor excuse for your foray to disengage from the deep of your encumbrance behold all our gold thousandfold bereave me ! decline truth ensign forever mine ! bereave me ! March in with ten legion whilst the crucial weapon be not the pillum but the feather hold in your hand pen in blood your tall-tales rule the forum alter it into the battlefield I , the spectral guise evoke these bare fear pester your conscript father I smile at my demise and while I die I cherish the root of my perseverance __________________ name thousandfold Artist Eluveitie album everything Remain [ as it never be ]